## Locations
      
<%- by_state.keys.each do |state| -%>
* [<%= state %>](#<%= state.downcase.gsub(/\s+/,'-') %>)
<%- end -%>

*Last Updated:* <%= current_timestamp %>

<%- by_state([Forecast::Aggregate, Forecast::Emoji]).each do |state, predictions| -%>
## <%= state %>
<%- number_of_forecasts = predictions.first.forecast.forecasts.length -%>

| Location | <%= predictions.first.forecast.forecasts.map{|tod, _| tod }.join(' | ') %> |
| <%= (['-'] * (number_of_forecasts + 1)).join(' | ') %> |            
<%- predictions.each do |prediction| -%>
| [<%= prediction.resort.name %>](<%= prediction.resort.url%>) | <%= prediction.forecast.forecasts[0...number_of_forecasts].map{|_, range| range }.join(' | ') %> |
<%- end -%>

<%- end -%>